dulates the Late-Stage Brain Response to Fear- and Stress-Provoking Pictures. Front Psychol. 2017;7:2055. Published 2017 Jan 10. doi:10.3389/fpsyg.2016.02055<br />\n<br />\n經其他大學審批後刊登係Frontiers in Psychology之中<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5223166/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC5223166%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kimt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=2192eb70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5223166/</a><br />\n<br />\n懶人包：文中以阿彌陀佛與其他普通名稱如聖誕老人作對照實驗，發現佛號真係張腦電波圖係有明顯分別的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pACrJ1N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpACrJ1N.jpg&h=b2bc52a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6w4vGU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6w4vGU.jpg&h=f5af9d16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望幫到大家釋除疑慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:04:15.000Z","msg":"放過佢？<br />\n<br />\n佢係到胡說佛經<br />\n令人誤會佛法<br />\n<br />\n佢唔害人已經係放過人<br />\n樓主連面對問題討論都唔敢喎<br />\n<br />\n仲要不停推廣佢自己間機構<br />\n<br />\n好難唔令人覺得佢別有用心"},{"pid":"4f166e0c45ad27680b3ba5442c4fa00705cba949","tid":2262143,"uid":176687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:05:59.000Z","msg":"淨空晚年又再用心支持 提倡「男女雙修」的密宗喇嘛教<br />\n<br />\n樓主咁落力推廣淨空<br />\n係咪會幫大家男女雙修<br />\n<br />\n係的一句<br />\n唔係即是對淨空沒信心<br />\n即是假"},{"pid":"42fe8555483259d28baa903f775c38f25f5a0cea","tid":2262143,"uid":213049,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ac5dffb15c793b7190548a487960d231a7861f3e","tid":2262143,"uid":176687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"254cd055b7f6de142628a59eac33354f4a8326b1","tid":2262143,"uid":213049,"like":1,"dislike":1,"sco