 />\n<br />\n另外近期啲人借攻擊淨空想去動搖成個淨土信仰，記得依法不依人<br />\n呢到就唔詳細討論住 有興趣先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87559dd72444fe13d544e6e91cecb9897c253259","tid":2262143,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b54ebfacd589e4e66b5cff22c75bc0f74d27efc6","tid":2262143,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":17,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T00:53:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGEaqd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGEaqd6.jpg&h=3119c1f7&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T05:12:43.000Z","msg":"阿彌陀佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}